{"tid":1951662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[運動方向] 其實諗唔到做乜都嘅你不如入黎一齊傾下計","createTime":"2020-03-31T06:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T08:00:30.000Z","uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac88ac41c0a42615bb01907d0ec84cee07242e3","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:11:05.000Z","msg":"有咩諗唔明 想放棄都總有原因<br />\n其實好多嘢可以傾 <br />\n工會、立會、街頭、經濟圈<br />\n當然夢境就唔使特別講<br />\n<br />\n係想知道大家對香港嘅想像<br />\n甚至你話自己想移民都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c4a6609c4a77201146b4ad16a1fe53c6b88eca","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人都好迷惘<br />\n可能覺得輸咖啦<br />\n<br />\n但當戴耀都講緊武裝革命嘅時候<br />\n大家又諗緊咩？<br />\n放棄？移民？定點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b66061a6fc44aea9c38da992379429eeffe1bc0","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee4bad13542dcebd08578a940316bb05acd4ff7","tid":1951662,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a480ef03241c55f3e71038fbb4667b697c0b94b5","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f24e87fff38cc18f1af9cb1c6d7c6086b36cb3a","tid":1951662,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2123abd37300d836d3305c1c1a008837520e68f8","tid":1951662,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"裝備自己，應付一切未知。"},{"pid":"56dded75ab3f300ae75eaa246d1c091d435d332f","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f24e87fff38cc18f1af9cb1c6d7c6086b36cb3a","tid":1951662,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得對於自己或香港未來嘅想像<br />\n可以好天馬行空<br />\n大家對於自己想點其實都唔清楚<br />\n好多疑問出現<br />\n好多灰心嘅情況<br />\n但如果永遠唔疏理<br />\n就一世都解決唔到"},{"pid":"400feb72e9124b5cb60d0e2ad66a8586bfd35fc3","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2123abd37300d836d3305c1c1a008837520e68f8","tid":1951662,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"裝備自己，應付一切未知。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n我覺嘅幾個範疇都係講緊裝備自己<br />\n當然仲未計好多文宣、包裝<br />\n甚至學多個新語言做對外文宣都係一個裝備黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論點都好<br />\n裝備自己永遠都唔會錯"},{"pid":"6dfe518be1b27c5e5a4a3d963e3fa6aa7751dd40","tid":1951662,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再鬥黃 唔好再批鬥 引你去批鬥既人全部係五毛<br />\n如果係紅底就唔值得討論 冷處理就得 唔好幫人出名<br />\n有時間批鬥不如做文宣"},{"pid":"82d2dcf2a569e9e54d5d218ec19d252a55724166","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dfe518be1b27c5e5a4a3d963e3fa6aa7751dd40","tid":1951662,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再鬥黃 唔好再批鬥 引你去批鬥既人全部係五毛<br />\n如果係紅底就唔值得討論 冷處理就得 唔好幫人出名<br />\n有時間批鬥不如做文宣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n就算我當唔係有人集團式式響連登做網軍(雖然我估點都會有)<br />\n<br />\n但起碼我地大家嘅睇法都係比一班人動搖緊<br />\n連登出現一種大規模嘅疲態<br />\n<br />\n我地的確係應該分享睇法<br />\n而唔係批鬥"},{"pid":"a6200348c25a5a15b3e1d0e8dc9287a24dfede15","tid":1951662,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff5c000ccde2cfdc27f5c746ec1484c831003d36","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61b6fa37237470e59d996a5afae7bd8d69885bf","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c636d6266b5b2592660cb88bf2f3bf079f7d6e87","tid":1951662,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"其實既然每一個政權都有倒台的時刻，與其諗點打，不如諗用咩取代佢"},{"pid":"6862f8ecdeb338dec4c656c07405147695c00bb7","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c636d6266b5b2592660cb88bf2f3bf079f7d6e87","tid":1951662,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"其實既然每一個政權都有倒台的時刻，與其諗點打，不如諗用咩取代佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n個想像係應該去到呢個程度<br />\n否則光復香港只係一個偽命題"},{"pid":"3164404dbba2d6eaaecb489fb12761eeb57454be","tid":1951662,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6862f8ecdeb338dec4c656c07405147695c00bb7","tid":1951662,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c636d6266b5b2592660cb88bf2f3bf079f7d6e87","tid":1951662,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"其實既然每一個政權都有倒台的時刻，與其諗點打，不如諗用咩取代佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"